Description: Fork of ShinyItemAnalysis with extended polytomous IRT model
    support (GRM, RSM, PCM, GPCM) alongside the existing NRM. Includes
    unified model selection, model comparison with LRT, Wright maps,
    observed proportion overlays, and mixed-category data handling.
    Based on the original package for psychometric analysis of educational
    tests, psychological assessments, health-related and other types of
    multi-item measurements, or ratings from multiple raters.
